        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="202" parent="1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:11px;&quot;&gt;• Step Library &amp; Fragment Store&lt;br&gt;• Strategy Assembler UI (step-assembler canvas)&lt;br&gt;• Strategy Compiler Service (JSON → BPMN XML)&lt;br&gt;• Deployment Pipeline (draft → review → active)&lt;br&gt;• Simulation Engine (replay historical journeys)&lt;br&gt;• Champion / Challenger Setup &amp; Results UI&lt;br&gt;• Strategy Version History &amp; Rollback&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="175" width="352" x="68" y="132" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="210" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e0f7fa;strokeColor=#00838F;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=13;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;" value="Task Configurator" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="218" width="368" x="443" y="97" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="210b" parent="1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;fontSize=9;fontStyle=2;fontColor=#00838F;" value="Task Configurator" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="14" width="200" x="451" y="117" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="211" parent="1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:11px;&quot;&gt;• Step Library Editor (create / edit / version step definitions)&lt;br&gt;• Human Task Type Configurator (task codes, routing rules, auto-assign logic — wraps Solon human-task-management)&lt;br&gt;• Drools Rule Builder (guided decision tables and rule conditions — wraps Solon Drools KIE via POST /drools-runtime/execute-stateless/{containerId})&lt;br&gt;• Task Form Designer (agent form fields per task type)&lt;br&gt;• Task Parameter Schema Editor (parameters each step exposes to Strategy Assembler)&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="175" width="352" x="451" y="132" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="220" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=13;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;" value="Policy Bundles" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="218" width="368" x="826" y="97" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="220b" parent="1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;fontSize=9;fontStyle=2;fontColor=#d79b00;" value="cross-section of all three layers" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="14" width="250" x="834" y="117" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="221" parent="1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:11px;&quot;&gt;• Vulnerability Management UI (flag capture, specialist view, category configurator, breathing space)&lt;br&gt;• Repay Plan &amp; I&amp;E UI (agent form, affordability result, arrangement options)&lt;br&gt;• Fraud &amp; Dispute UI (dispute registration, investigation, account freeze)&lt;br&gt;• Breathing Space Management UI (statutory periods, expiry, audit log)&lt;br&gt;• Policy Bundle packaging (groups process + task + foundation config per bundle)&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="175" width="352" x="834" y="132" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="230" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=13;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;" value="Agent &amp; Operations UI" vertex="1">
