        <mxCell id="302" parent="1" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px;&quot;&gt;• Contact Orchestration Service&lt;br&gt;• Channel Adapters (SMS / Email / Letter / Dialler)&lt;br&gt;• Dialler Integration Service (bidirectional CTI)&lt;br&gt;• Contact Suppression Service — signals Solon via Kafka: irm.bpmn-engine.create-suppression / release-suppression (NOT a REST API)&lt;br&gt;• Template Management Service&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
